data.text:
Finland is one of the countries that took the space cash in the Season Thirteen episode, "Pinewood Derby". Its capital and largest city is Helsinki.

Background[]

The Prime Minister Matti Vanhanen had reservations about stealing Baby Fark McGee-zax space cash.

It was nuked by the other countries because the people of Finland wanted to tell the Intergalactic Police about the human race stealing the "space cash".
